    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 6th level, home can be wherever you are. During a short or long rest, you can invoke the shadowy power of the Gloaming Court to help guard your respite. At the start of the rest, you touch a point in space, and an invisible, 30-foot-radius sphere of magic appears, centered on that point. &amp;Reference[rule=Totalcover]{Total cover} blocks the sphere.</p><p>While within the sphere, you and your allies gain a +5 bonus to Dexterity (&amp;Reference[skill=Stealth]) and Wisdom (&amp;Reference[skill=Perception]) checks, and any light from open flames in the sphere (a campfire, torches, or the like) isn't visible outside it.</p><p>The sphere vanishes at the end of the rest or when you leave the sphere.</p></div>",
